		"description": "<p><em>(Requires attunement by a spellcaster)</em></p><p>This wand has 7 charges. While holding it, you can use an action to expend 1 of its charges to cast the @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.04nMsTWkIFvkbXlY]{Polymorph} spell (save DC 15) from it.</p><p>The wand regains 1d6 + 1 expended charges daily at dawn. If you expend the wand's last charge, roll a d20. On a 1, the wand crumbles into ashes and is destroyed.</p>",
